subproject.description:
(1) Tool kit that simulates taxes and social benefits developed and shared to assist decision makers in LAC in implementing pro-poor and equitable policies.
(2) Efforts coordinated through regional and sub regional forums for experience sharing and policy dialogue on Inclusive growth.
subproject.title: Inclusive Growth in Latin Amer
